== Jamal OpenAI module Completion API
{%@import samples.jim%}
{%@define PROMPT=Short Summary of EPAM's 2018Q4 Earnings Call:%}

With the OpenAI module, you can include text generated by the OpenAI API into your documents.
That way you can ask OpenAI to complete your text, answer questions, and so on.

* For example, asking the prompt below __"{%PROMPT%}"__ will result in the following text:

{%@define openai:model=babbage%}\
{%@options ~openai:sealed%}\
{%@define openai:seed=126%}\
{%#json:define epam_results={%openai:completion |
"prompt": "{%PROMPT%}",
"max_tokens": 100,
"temperature": 0.2
%}\
%}\

{%@json:get epam_results/choices/0/text | epam_results%}